title: 166: Scouting Competition winners, perfect pairings and interviews
itunes:title: 166: Scouting Competition winners, perfect pairings and interviews
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss the latest NFL Draft news including Sidney Jones’ injury, Reuben Foster’s dismissal from the Combine and some surprising free agent signings. Bucky talks to Cal quarterback Davis Webb about his journey to the NFL and Texans general manager Rick Smith about building his team. DJ and Bucky also reveal the winners of the Move The Sticks Scouting Competition and also reveal the perfect pairings for the first two draft picks of every AFC North team.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
